#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.cast"
msgstr "# triton.language.cast"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:4
msgid "将张量转换为指定的数据类型，支持数值类型转换、位级别重解释（bitcast）、浮点降精度舍入模式，以及Ascend扩展的整数溢出处理模式。"
msgstr "Convert the tensor to the specified data type, supporting numeric type conversion, bit-level reinterpretation (bitcast), floating-point precision reduction rounding mode, and Ascend-extended integer overflow handling mode."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.cast(input, dtype, fp_downcast_rounding=None, bitcast=False)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `input.cast(dtype, fp_downcast_rounding=None, bitcast=False)` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.cast(input, dtype, fp_downcast_rounding=None, bitcast=False)` - Function call form\n"
"- `input.cast(dtype, fp_downcast_rounding=None, bitcast=False)` - Member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:12
msgid ""
"- 数值类型转换：整型<->整型、浮点<->浮点、整型<->浮点\n"
"- 位级别重解释（bitcast）：不改变比特，只改变解释类型\n"
"- 浮点降精度支持舍入模式：`rtne`（默认，四舍六入五成双）、`rtz`（向零）\n"
"- 整数转换（Ascend 扩展）支持溢出模式：`trunc`（截断，默认）、`saturate`（饱和）\n"
msgstr ""
"- Numeric type conversion: integer <-> integer, float <-> float, integer <-> float\n"
"- Bit-level reinterpretation (bitcast): bits unchanged, only the interpretation type changes\n"
"- Float precision reduction supports rounding modes: `rtne` (default, round to nearest, ties to even), `rtz` (toward zero)\n"
"- Integer conversion (Ascend extension) supports overflow modes: `trunc` (truncation, default), `saturate` (saturation)\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 输入张量 |\n"
"| dtype | tl.dtype | 是 | 目标数据类型 |\n"
"| fp_downcast_rounding | str | 否 | 仅对浮点降精度有效，`rtne` 或 `rtz` |\n"
"| bitcast | bool | 否 | 是否执行位级别重解释，默认 False |\n"
"| overflow_mode | str | 否 | Ascend 扩展：整数溢出处理，`trunc` 或 `saturate` |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | Input tensor |\n"
"| dtype | tl.dtype | Yes | Target data type |\n"
"| fp_downcast_rounding | str | No | Only valid for floating-point downcasting, `rtne` or `rtz` |\n"
"| bitcast | bool | No | Whether to perform bit-level reinterpretation, default False |\n"
"| overflow_mode | str | No | Ascend extension: integer overflow handling, `trunc` or `saturate` |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与dtype参数指定的目标类型相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 根据bitcast参数决定是否进行位级别重解释\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor\n"
"- **Shape:** Same as the input tensor\n"
"- **Data type:** Same as the target type specified by the `dtype` parameter\n"
"- **Memory layout:** Whether to perform bit-level reinterpretation is determined by the `bitcast` parameter\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cast.md:26
msgid ""
"- `fp_downcast_rounding` 仅在浮点降精度时可设置，否则将报错\n"
"- `bitcast=True` 时不进行数值转换，忽略舍入/溢出模式\n"
"- `overflow_mode` 仅对整型有意义（Ascend 扩展）\n"
msgstr ""
"- `fp_downcast_rounding` can only be set when downcasting floating-point precision; otherwise, an error will be reported.\n"
"- When `bitcast=True`, no numerical conversion is performed, and rounding/overflow modes are ignored.\n"
"- `overflow_mode` is only meaningful for integer types (Ascend extension).\n"

